brute force attempt into a DoS attack against our login system, but it would not compromise the validity of user passwords. We're currently working on rate-limiting logins on our front end.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eThanks for your report!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe use bcrypt with a sufficiently high work factor which would make brute forcing of a reasonable password unfeasibly slow. At the moment, this would likely turn a password brute force attempt into a DoS attack against our login system, but it would not compromise the validity of user passwords. We\u0026#39;re currently working on rate-limiting logins on our front end.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:46:06.869Z","updated_at":"2014-04-11T00:46:06.869Z","actor":{"username":"russss","cleared":false,"url":"/russss","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/004/786/b539136875027662b8b5aefbacce2c7d8ab11837_original.jpeg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"irccloud","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":29854,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi sir,\n\nAm I getting it right sir? My only concern is, an attacker is not being stop to guess the password of an existing user in IRCcloud.\n\nNo mechanism to stop an attacker who is guessing a user password multiple times. I believe, this has nothing to do with IRCcloud's login system being attacked thru DOS.\n\nYou mention of the rate-limiting login sir, this is I believe my point. Isn't this a valid security issue? \n\nI believe thru this, user data could be compromise in some way.\n\nThank you very much sir.\n\nBest,\nClifford","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eHi sir,\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAm I getting it right sir? My only concern is, an attacker is not being stop to guess the password of an existing user in IRCcloud.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eNo mechanism to stop an attacker who is guessing a user password multiple times. I believe, this has nothing to do with IRCcloud\u0026#39;s login system being attacked thru DOS.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou mention of the rate-limiting login sir, this is I believe my point. Isn\u0026#39;t this a valid security issue? \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI believe thru this, user data could be compromise in some way.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThank you very much sir.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBest,\u003cbr\u003e\nClifford\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-04-14T02:08:40.875Z","updated_at":"2014-04-14T02:08:40.875Z","actor":{"username":"techintheprovince","cleared":false,"url":"/techintheprovince","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/002/212/0c2d20f98e4a3849bc805af34a9a8bb7d9935a85_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"irccloud","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":29857,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"[ quote] It's recommended to implement some type of account lockout after a defined number of incorrect password attempts. \n","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003e[ quote] It\u0026#39;s recommended to implement some type of account lockout after a defined number of incorrect password attempts. \u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-04-14T02:13:49.821Z","updated_at":"2014-04-14T02:13:49.821Z","actor":{"username":"techintheprovince","cleared":false,"url":"/techintheprovince","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/002/212/0c2d20f98e4a3849bc805af34a9a8bb7d9935a85_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db